Vantablack HeadDB is a multi-license project forked from
SilentDevelopment/HeadDB.

The license for each source area is:

- headdb-api: Apache License 2.0
- headdb-core: Apache License 2.0
- src/main/java/com/vantablack4/headdb: proprietary Vantablack4 internal code
- src/main/resources and build/CI files: proprietary Vantablack4 internal code

The full Apache 2.0 text is available in:

- LICENSES/Apache-2.0.txt

The GPL-3.0-or-later text is retained under LICENSES only for historical
upstream reference. The Fabric platform layer in this branch does not copy the
upstream Paper platform module.

Unless a file states otherwise, files are licensed under the license of the
source area they belong to.
